Company Overview of Phoenix Investment Adviser LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Phoenix Investment Adviser LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also provides its services to corporations or other businesses. The firm invests in fixed income markets. It primarily invests in securities and other obligations of companies that are experiencing significant financial or business distress, including companies that may be involved in bankruptcy or other reorganization and liquidation proceedings, i.e. distressed and stressed securities, primarily corporate bonds. The firm employs event driven strategies to make its investments. It employs fundamental analysis with focus on bottom-up analysis to m...
Phoenix Investment Adviser LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also provides its services to corporations or other businesses. The firm invests in fixed income markets. It primarily invests in securities and other obligations of companies that are experiencing significant financial or business distress, including companies that may be involved in bankruptcy or other reorganization and liquidation proceedings, i.e. distressed and stressed securities, primarily corporate bonds. The firm employs event driven strategies to make its investments. It employs fundamental analysis with focus on bottom-up analysis to make its investments. The firm obtains external research to complement its in-house research. Phoenix Investment Adviser LLC was founded on May 22, 2003 and is based in New York City.
Detailed Description


